Version: 1.0.756
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: libxi6, libxrender1, libxtst6
Maintainer: Benjamin Sautner <ben@krill.zone>
Description: Krill Desktop Control Application
 Krill Desktop is a Compose Multiplatform GUI application for monitoring
 and controlling Krill servers on your network.
 Requires Java 21 or later to be installed separately.
